OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy with patchy rain or
OL,6,Fdrizzle. This clears as bright or
OL,7,Fsunny spells develop and many places
OL,8,Fbecome dry with only the occasional
OL,9,Fshower from mid-morning.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FBright or clear spells
OL,12,Fcontinue as showers die during the
OL,13,Fevening. Cloud will increase towards
OL,14,Fmidnight and outbreaks of locally
OL,15,Fheavy rain spread northeast towards
OL,16,Fmorning.
OL,17,
OL,18,CThursday:FCloudy with outbreaks of
OL,19,Flocally heavy rain. This rain will
OL,20,Fclear during the afternoon and sunny
OL,21,Fspells follow towards the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
